metadata.name: Musafir
metadata.description:
This picture was taken just outside my hometown Amritsar, Punjab (India) on 15 December 2015. 'Musafir' is a punjabi word which translates to traveller. An orthodox Nihang Singh can be seen walking down the road in a sunny winter afternoon.

Dimensions : 1536 × 2304
Shot on Nikon D5300 with 50mm
